The paper discusses the visualization of proofs, which is a topic related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). It also involves machine learning techniques for tree visualization, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the layout of inferences, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and computational logic (cs.CL). Finally, the paper describes the integration of the proposed visualization technique into PROOFTOOL, which is a software engineering tool (cs.SE).
